&lt;p&gt;The fire is slowly dying,&lt;br /&gt;
And, my dear, we&#039;re still good-bying,&lt;br /&gt;
But as long as you love me so,&lt;br /&gt;
Let It Snow! Let It Snow! Let It Snow!&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
